column2: SELECT p.ra, p.dec, p.modelFlux_u, p.modelFlux_g, p.modelFlux_r, p.modelFlux_i, p.modelFlux_z, p.modelFluxIvar_u, p.modelFluxIvar_g, p.modelFluxIvar_r, p.modelFluxIvar_i, p.modelFluxIvar_z, d.w1flux, d.w2flux, d.w3flux, d.w4flux, d.w1sigflux, d.w2sigflux, d.w3sigflux, d.w4sigflux FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on p.ObjID=c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr=d.cntr
